article:
'KIND' may refer to:

* KIND (AM), a radio station (1010 AM) licensed to Independence, Kansas,
  United States
* KIND-FM, a radio station (94.9 FM) licensed to Elk City, Kansas, United States
* KBIK, a radio station (102.9 FM) licensed to Independence, Kansas, United
  States that held the call sign KIND-FM from 1980 to 2010
* Indianapolis International Airport, an airport located in Indianapolis,
  Indiana, United States
